{"tid":528463,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"語言JJ 有無人覺得學外語係一種好正既興趣？","createTime":"2018-01-13T19:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T19:16:57.000Z","uid":11261,"like":44,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9a754baed3af93821ffb291336b011a299d663","tid":528463,"uid":11261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:28:05.000Z","msg":"自己喜歡日本，學左多年日文，發覺日本易學難精，睇小說，同一語境可以用好多唔同既詞語表達，越研究越覺得有趣<br />\n<br />\n仲學緊西班牙文 ，覺得發音好好聽又多人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n遲啲打算學意大利文，好似好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同覺得發音又係好聽，本身對羅馬帝國歷史有啲興趣，雖然真正羅馬人可能已經絕種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過西文同意文有啲接近，所以遲啲先學<br />\n<br />\n巴絲有無學開咩冷門外語可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者識好多種語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112481e2886309268f20e9e0c0c4333eb930364c","tid":528463,"uid":44073,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:36:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71b7a4c12964973edb6183e68a64d7f012341f85","tid":528463,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:39:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfdccaa25289619a26489b8224e2c70ae2483ea2","tid":528463,"uid":16719,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:44:28.000Z","msg":"涯hea嚇加鹽"},{"pid":"bc9a4df7baeab4fcbae7476524af934fd23bd639","tid":528463,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:45:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0d7a6823569b43bfcfe1d927d5d20fc1128903d","tid":528463,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:45:55.000Z","msg":"想同日本人試下傾計學日文<br />\n男女老幼都得<br />\n利伸: 識say hi 同 say goodbye 日文"},{"pid":"7bb7ee12f540a785f7b51b0c1506b9ef1b2cd996","tid":528463,"uid":71418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e0d7a6823569b43bfcfe1d927d